just shove it in as fixed predictor



::: {.cell layout-align="center"}

```{.r .cell-code}
df <- read_csv("https://uoepsy.github.io/data/dapr3_tgu.csv")

df <- df |> group_by(patient) |>
  mutate(
    physm = mean(phys),
    physdev = phys - mean(phys)
  ) |> ungroup()

mod <- lmer(tgu ~ hospital + physm + physdev + 
              (1 + physdev | patient),
            data = df)
```
