# ℹ 3 variables: school <chr>, child <chr>, n <int>
```


:::
:::




Phew!  

Okay, let's just fit an intercept-only model:  



::: {.cell layout-align="center"}

```{.r .cell-code}
pvt_null <- lmer(PVT ~ 1 +  (1 | school/child), data = pvt)
summary(pvt_null)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

